{"ja162:0.1":"Jataka ","ja162:0.2":"Dukanipata ","ja162:0.3":"Santhavavagga ","ja162:0.4":"2. Santhavajataka ","ja162:1.1":"“Na santhavasma paramatthi papiyo, ","ja162:1.2":"Yo santhavo kapurisena hoti; ","ja162:1.3":"Santappito sappina payasena, ","ja162:1.4":"Kicchakatam pannakutim adayhi. ","ja162:2.1":"Na santhavasma paramatthi seyyo, ","ja162:2.2":"Yo santhavo sappurisena hoti; ","ja162:2.3":"Sihassa byagghassa ca dipino ca, ","ja162:2.4":"Sama mukham lehati santhavena”ti. ","ja162:3.1":"Santhavajatakam dutiyam. "}